{"tid":439381,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"IPHONE相簿裡面D相係度但相簿唔見左","createTime":"2017-10-17T17:47:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T03:52:56.000Z","uid":16087,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3d6da1528f7381c2da79f0ca20fb245816c48698","tid":439381,"uid":16087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T17:47:42.000Z","msg":"今日用用下機佢死機之後復原D相<br />\n咁就復原好晒,見返D相<br />\n但IPHONE相片APP到睇唔到某D相簿, E.G:IG相簿,自己同步個D相既相簿<br />\n但唔用相簿模式睇,淨係用相片睇係有晒D圖係度...<br />\n之後我再用IG禁POST相 揀相個度可以轉相簿,亦都見到之前D相簿係晒度,D相冇唔見, 所以 其他APP可以見到我IPHONE相片APP入面見唔到既相簿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問各位巴打點樣係IPHONE相簿APP整返D相簿出黎?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似講到1999,希望有人明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d86faa4c9da1dad1362df87345952705f9f5c0f9","tid":439381,"uid":16087,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T17:51:50.000Z","msg":"例如我禁IPHONE相機菲林,入面係冇ABC呢個相簿,但見到D相係到<br />\n<br />\n再用IG禁菲林相簿,係見到ABC呢個相簿<br />\n只係IPHONE個相機菲林APP係冇個相簿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff1b1